INDEED.

71
00:05:17,427 --> 00:05:19,794
CALIBAN, LEND ME YOUR POWER.

72
00:05:19,827 --> 00:05:21,894
OOH, GLADLY, ARTHUR.

73
00:05:21,927 --> 00:05:27,560
BY ORDER OF THE GRIGORI,
ADVISERS OF THE TRUE CROSS,

74
