THE BOY SWORDSMANSHIP.

83
00:05:55,127 --> 00:05:57,627
SURELY YOU DON'T INTEND
TO FULFILL THE DYING WISH...

84
00:05:57,660 --> 00:06:00,194
OF THE MOST UNFIT PALADIN
IN HISTORY.

85
00:06:00,227 --> 00:06:01,994
LIKE I SAID,
YOU BALD-ASS BASTARD--

86
00:06:02,027 --> 00:06:04,760
