REGARDLESS, THE GRIGORI'S
ORDERS ARE ABSOLUTE.

88
00:06:09,427 --> 00:06:11,094
EVEN FOR SOMEONE LIKE YOU.

89
00:06:11,127 --> 00:06:12,727
