I CAN'T WAIT.

96
00:06:28,094 --> 00:06:32,427
SHURA, YOU'RE A WITNESS,
SO IF YOU DON'T MIND,
YOU'RE COMING ALONG WITH ME.

97
00:06:32,460 --> 00:06:35,494
THE SPAWN OF SATAN COMES TOO.
I'LL NEED HIM AS EVIDENCE.

98
00:06:35,527 --> 00:06:37,927
EXCUSE ME.
I'D LIKE TO COME TOO.

99
00:06:37,960 --> 00:06:41,427
[MEPHISTO] I'M SORRY,
BUT YOU SHOULD STAY HERE
AND LOOK AFTER YOUR STUDENTS.

100
00:06:41,460 --> 00:06:43,060
LIKE A GOOD TEACHER.

101
00:06:44,360 --> 00:06:46,994
