ANY LONGER...

102
00:06:47,027 --> 00:06:48,727
NOW THAT HIS SWORD IS DAMAGED.

103
00:06:48,760 --> 00:06:50,460
[GASPS]

104
00:06:53,994 --> 00:06:56,060
WELL, ANGEL,
SHALL WE GO?

105
00:07:02,060 --> 00:07:04,327
[FOOTSTEPS RECEDING]

106
00:07:09,678 --> 00:07:12,812
[MAN]
THE COURT WILL NOW HEAR
THE CASE OF MEPHISTO PHELES,

107
00:07:12,845 --> 00:07:16,712
PRECEPT OF THE JAPAN BRANCH
OF THE KNIGHTS
OF THE TRUE CROSS.

108
00:07:16,745 --> 00:07:21,812
I, TIMOTHÉ TIMOWAN,
CHIEF JUSTICE OF THE ORDER,
AND ARTHUR AUGUSTE ANGEL,

109
00:07:21,845 --> 00:07:25,212
THE CURRENT PALADIN,
WILL CARRY OUT
THE INTERROGATION.

110
00:07:25,245 --> 00:07:31,445
PRESIDING ARE THE GRIGORI,
ADVISERS TO THE KNIGHTS
OF THE TRUE CROSS.

111
00:07:31,478 --> 00:07:34,678
SIR PHELES,
LET'S GET STRAIGHT
TO THE POINT.

112
00:07:34,712 --> 00:07:38,412
IS THIS CREATURE
I SEE BEFORE ME
THE SON OF SATAN?

113
00:07:38,445 --> 00:07:40,812
THAT HE IS, YOUR HONOR.

114
00:07:40,845 --> 00:07:44,278
I SIMPLY CAN'T HIDE THE TRUTH
ANY LONGER.

115
00:07:44,312 --> 00:07:49,045
FIFTEEN YEARS AGO
MY BROTHER RIN WAS BORN.

116
00:07:49,078 --> 00:07:52,378
HIS MOTHER WAS HUMAN.
SATAN WAS HIS FATHER.

117
00:07:52,412 --> 00:07:56,145
AS A RESULT, HE'S INHERITED
THE POWER
OF SATAN'S BLUE FLAMES.

118
00:07:56,178 --> 00:07:57,978
[ALL GASP]

119
00:07:58,012 --> 00:08:01,912
UM, I DON'T MEAN TO PRY,
BUT YOU AND HE ARE TWINS.

120
00:08:01,945 --> 00:08:04,412
SO DOES THAT MEAN
YOU HAVE THAT POWER TOO?

121
00:08:04,445 --> 00:08:06,278
NO. I DIDN'T INHERIT
THE BLUE FLAMES.

122
00:08:06,312 --> 00:08:09,212
I HAVE TO GET EXAMINED
FOR IT EVERY DAY THOUGH.

123
00:08:09,245 --> 00:08:11,345
AS FAR AS I KNOW,
I'M STILL HUMAN.

124
00:08:11,378 --> 00:08:17,312
[WOMAN] TO CLARIFY, YURI EGIN,
JUNIOR EXORCIST SECOND CLASS,
GAVE BIRTH TO SATAN'S SON.

125
00:08:17,345 --> 00:08:21,045
BUT THE REPORT STATES
THAT FUJIMOTO KILLED HIM
WITH THE KOMA SWORD.

126
00:08:21,078 --> 00:08:23,845
AND NOW YOU'RE SAYING
THAT REPORT WAS FALSE?

127
00:08:23,878 --> 00:08:26,778
YES. THE FACT IS
TWO CHILDREN WERE BORN,

128
00:08:26,812 --> 00:08:29,345
BUT ONLY ONE
INHERITED THE POWER OF SATAN.

129
00:08:29,378 --> 00:08:32,045
AND THAT CHILD
IS THE ONE BEFORE YOU NOW.

130
00:08:33,212 --> 00:08:34,845
HE WOULD'VE TURNED
INTO A DEMON,

131
00:08:34,878 --> 00:08:38,112
SO I SEALED THE SOURCE
OF HIS POWER,
HIS DEMONIC HEART,

132
00:08:38,145 --> 00:08:40,078
WITHIN THE KOMA SWORD.

133
00:08:40,112 --> 00:08:45,278
EVENTUALLY, HIS POWER
BECAME TOO GREAT
FOR THE KOMA SWORD TO CONTAIN.

134
00:08:45,312 --> 00:08:48,278
IT AWOKE INSIDE HIM
ABOUT THREE MONTHS AGO.

135
00:08:48,312 --> 00:08:51,012
THREE MONTHS AGO?
AND UNTIL THAT DAY,

136
00:08:51,045 --> 00:08:54,578
RIN GREW UP NOT KNOWING
THE TRUTH ABOUT HIMSELF.

137
00:08:54,612 --> 00:08:56,078
[THINKING]
BUT THAT'S WHEN--

138
00:08:56,112 --> 00:09:00,378
DON'T JUMP TO CONCLUSIONS.
I'M NOT A DEMON.
GOT IT?

139
00:09:00,412 --> 00:09:02,512
THAT'S WHY HE WAS ANGRY.

140
00:09:02,545 --> 00:09:05,545
DO YOU KNOW WHAT THEY'RE
GONNA DO TO RIN?

141
00:09:05,578 --> 00:09:08,745
DEPENDING ON THE VERDICT,
THEY COULD DECIDE
TO EXECUTE HIM.

142
00:09:08,778 --> 00:09:13,112
REALLY?
ONCE HE'S CONSUMED
BY THE POWER OF THE FLAMES,

143
00:09:13,145 --> 00:09:14,645
HE'LL TRANSFORM INTO A DEMON.

144
00:09:14,678 --> 00:09:18,712
IF THAT HAPPENS,
HE CAN'T BE ALLOWED
TO LIVE IN THIS WORLD ANYMORE.

145
00:09:18,745 --> 00:09:22,545
BUT, YUKI, YOU SOUND
LIKE YOU DON'T EVEN CARE
IF RIN DIES.

146
00:09:22,578 --> 00:09:24,745
I NEVER SAID THAT!

147
00:09:24,778 --> 00:09:25,845
I DIDN'T.

148
00:09:25,878 --> 00:09:28,478
I JUST DON'T WANT HIM
TO SUFFER ANYMORE.

149
00:09:28,512 --> 00:09:32,412
EVEN IF RIN WANTS TO,
HE CAN'T GO BACK TO LIVING
A NORMAL HUMAN LIFE.

150
00:09:32,445 --> 00:09:34,912
ESPECIALLY NOW...

151
00:09:34,945 --> 00:09:36,212
THAT HIS SWORD'S
CRACKED.

152
00:09:36,245 --> 00:09:38,312
WHAT? KURIKARA'S BLADE
IS CRACKED?

153
00:09:38,345 --> 00:09:40,012
WHAT DID YOU JUST CALL IT?

154
00:09:40,045 --> 00:09:42,545
HUH?
I'VE ALWAYS CALLED THIS
THE KOMA SWORD,

155
00:09:42,578 --> 00:09:44,245
BUT YOU CALLED IT
KURIKARA.

156
00:09:44,278 --> 00:09:47,278
HOW DO YOU
EVEN KNOW THAT?

157
00:09:47,312 --> 00:09:50,145
KURIKARA.
IT'S THE SWORD'S REAL NAME.

158
00:09:50,178 --> 00:09:53,745
AT LEAST THAT'S WHAT EVERYONE
CALLED IT BACK WHEN IT WAS ONE
OF MY TEMPLE'S TREASURES.

159
00:09:53,778 --> 00:09:55,845
[GASPS]

160
00:09:55,878 --> 00:09:59,312
BON, DO YOU THINK
IF WE BROUGHT IT
TO THE YOSHIKUNIS,

161
00:09:59,345 --> 00:10:00,878
THEY MIGHT BE ABLE
TO DO SOMETHING?

162
00:10:00,912 --> 00:10:02,345
YOSHIKUNIS?

163
00:10:02,378 --> 00:10:05,212
THE FAMILY OF SWORDSMITHS
WHO FORGED KURIKARA.

164
00:10:05,245 --> 00:10:07,378
THERE'S ONLY ONE
OF THEM LEFT NOW.

165
00:10:07,412 --> 00:10:09,978
DO YOU THINK
THEY MIGHT BE ABLE
TO FIX IT?

166
00:10:10,012 --> 00:10:12,378
WELL, I DON'T KNOW.

167
00:10:12,412 --> 00:10:14,045
ARE YOU KIDDING?
[ALL]
HUH?

168
00:10:14,078 --> 00:10:17,678
THAT'S CRAZY.
DO YOU GUYS EVEN KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT?

169
00:10:17,712 --> 00:10:20,178
WHAT ARE YOU THINKING?
AREN'T YOU SCARED?

170
00:10:20,212 --> 00:10:22,478
FIX THE SWORD?
ARE YOU SERIOUS?

171
00:10:22,512 --> 00:10:24,312
WHY ON EARTH WOULD ANYONE
WANT TO DO THAT?

172
00:10:24,345 --> 00:10:27,045
[SHIEMI]
BECAUSE RIN IS OUR--
[MIWA] HE'S THE SON OF SATAN!

173
00:10:28,512 --> 00:10:31,112
I KNOW HOW YOU ALL MUST FEEL.
I UNDERSTAND WHY.

174
00:10:31,145 --> 00:10:35,378
BUT PLEASE, IF THERE'S A WAY
TO SAVE MY BROTHER,
I NEED YOUR HELP.

175
00:10:35,412 --> 00:10:36,845
PLEASE.

176
00:10:39,645 --> 00:10:43,045
- CUT IT OUT.
- SUGURO.

177
00:10:43,078 --> 00:10:44,712
[WOMAN]
SIR PHELES,

178
00:10:44,745 --> 00:10:48,012
YOU ADMIT TO HAVING
SHIRO FUJIMOTO
RAISE THE BOY IN SECRET.

179
00:10:48,045 --> 00:10:49,945
MY QUESTION
TO YOU IS, WHY?

180
00:10:49,978 --> 00:10:51,945
EXPLAIN YOURSELF.

181
00:10:51,978 --> 00:10:54,445
TO FIGHT SATAN.

182
00:10:54,478 --> 00:10:56,878
I WAS TURNING HIM INTO A WEAPON
FOR THE ORDER.

183
00:10:56,912 --> 00:10:58,278
WHAT DID YOU SAY?
[PEOPLE GASPING]

184
00:10:58,312 --> 00:11:00,412
YOU'D USE THAT BOY
TO FIGHT SATAN?

185
00:11:00,445 --> 00:11:01,912
[WOMAN]
THAT'S MONSTROUS!

186
00:11:01,945 --> 00:11:03,678
HE'S LYING!

187
00:11:03,712 --> 00:11:07,645
I ADVISE THE COURT
TO THINK TWICE
BEFORE BELIEVING THIS SWINDLER.

188
00:11:07,678 --> 00:11:12,178
LADIES AND GENTLEMEN,
SURELY YOU HAVEN'T FORGOTTEN
WHAT PHELES IS.

189
00:11:12,212 --> 00:11:15,145
LIES ARE THE STOCK AND TRADE
OF HIS KIND.

190
00:11:21,278 --> 00:11:23,412
[SIGHS]
OKAY, LET'S GET GOING.

191
00:11:23,445 --> 00:11:25,745
COME ON, TAKE US
TO THIS YOSHIKUNI PERSON.

192
00:11:25,778 --> 00:11:28,178
HELLO? YOU GUYS
ARE THE ONLY ONES
WHO KNOW HOW TO GET THERE.

193
00:11:28,212 --> 00:11:29,912
KAMIKI.
WHATEVER.

194
00:11:29,945 --> 00:11:33,745
I'M TIRED OF LISTENING
TO EVERYONE TALKING
AND NOT DOING ANYTHING.

195
00:11:33,778 --> 00:11:35,912
[DOOR OPENS, CLOSES]
WELL, BON?

196
00:11:35,945 --> 00:11:38,078
[SIGHS]

197
00:11:44,845 --> 00:11:46,578
[SHIMA]
ONE SECOND,
WE'RE IN KYOTO.

198
00:11:46,612 --> 00:11:50,312
THIS KEY CAN TRANSPORT US
TO ANY CITY INSTANTLY...

199
00:11:50,345 --> 00:11:53,045
AS LONG AS IT HAS
A RELIGIOUS SITE.

200
00:11:53,078 --> 00:11:55,745
LEAD THE WAY.
MM.

201
00:11:55,778 --> 00:11:57,078
YEAH.

202
00:12:03,278 --> 00:12:05,545
[HAMMERING]

203
00:12:21,978 --> 00:12:24,012
[SIGHS]
HMM?

204
00:12:27,245 --> 00:12:28,512
RYUGI!

205
00:12:28,545 --> 00:12:31,178
RYUGI!
[GRUNTS]
HEY!

206
00:12:31,212 --> 00:12:33,712
- OKAY.
- [GIGGLING]

207
00:12:33,745 --> 00:12:35,545
[GROANING]

208
00:12:46,444 --> 00:12:48,777
[CRICKETS CHIRPING]

209
00:12:48,810 --> 00:12:51,310
[CHATTERING]

210
00:12:57,044 --> 00:12:58,410
[GASPS]

211
00:12:59,282 --> 00:13:01,816
HEY, GUYS?

212
00:13:04,082 --> 00:13:05,416
[GRUNTS]

213
00:13:06,749 --> 00:13:08,916
[SHOUTING]

214
00:13:11,216 --> 00:13:13,749
[SCREAMING]

215
00:13:16,982 --> 00:13:18,816
[WOMAN]
NO ONE ARGUES THE FACT...

216
00:13:18,849 --> 00:13:20,982
THAT WE VIEW DEMONS
AS OUR ENEMY.

217
00:13:21,016 --> 00:13:24,649
HOWEVER, WE'VE LEARNED MUCH
FROM THEM OVER THE CENTURIES.

218
