COUNTERMEASURES WE'VE DEVELOPED.

219
00:13:28,682 --> 00:13:34,049
EVEN SO, NONE OF THAT CAN EVEN
BEGIN TO DISPEL THE SUSPICIONS
OF TREACHERY BY SIR PHELES.

220
00:13:34,082 --> 00:13:38,016
AND YET HE HAS COOPERATED
WITH THE ORDER FOR 200 YEARS.

221
00:13:38,049 --> 00:13:41,749
SURELY THAT IS REASON
ENOUGH TO TRUST HIM.

222
00:13:41,782 --> 00:13:43,882
[ANGEL]
THIS DEMON CONSPIRED
WITH SHIRO FUJIMOTO...

223
00:13:43,916 --> 00:13:45,416
TO RAISE THE SON OF SATAN.

224
00:13:45,449 --> 00:13:48,216
THAT FACT IS INDISPUTABLE.

225
00:13:48,249 --> 00:13:51,916
[SUGURO]
SHE'S 11TH GENERATION YOSHIKUNI.

226
00:13:51,949 --> 00:13:54,449
DESCENDED
FROM THE SWORDSMITH
WHO FORGED KURIKARA.

227
00:13:54,482 --> 00:13:56,549
A FEMALE SWORDSMITH?

228
00:13:56,582 --> 00:13:58,516
THAT SHOULDN'T BE
SO SURPRISING.

229
00:13:58,549 --> 00:14:03,516
WHY, DURING THE MID-EDO PERIOD,
THERE WAS A MASTER SWORDSMITH
KNOWN AS LADY KUNISHIGE.

230
00:14:03,549 --> 00:14:07,416
THEIR NAMES MIGHT NOT BE
IN THE HISTORY BOOKS, BUT I KNOW
THERE WERE LOTS MORE LIKE HER.

231
00:14:07,449 --> 00:14:09,282
THE LADY REALLY KNOWS
HER STUFF.

232
00:14:09,316 --> 00:14:12,782
HELL, THIS CHICK'S GONNA BE
THE NEXT ONE TO LEAVE HER MARK
ON THE WORLD.

233
00:14:12,816 --> 00:14:14,682
WHO ARE YOU CALLING "CHICK,"
YOU POSEUR?

234
00:14:14,716 --> 00:14:15,982
[GROANS]
WATCH IT!

235
00:14:16,016 --> 00:14:18,982
[CHUCKLES]
BON'S BEEN PUT
IN HIS PLACE.

236
00:14:19,016 --> 00:14:21,982
MY FATHER AND I GO
TO RYUGI'S TEMPLE
TO CLEAN STUFF,

237
00:14:22,016 --> 00:14:23,882
SO WE'VE KNOWN EACH OTHER
SINCE WE WERE LITTLE KIDS.

238
00:14:23,916 --> 00:14:26,349
YOU SHOULD'VE SEEN HIM.
HE WAS SO CUTE.

239
00:14:26,382 --> 00:14:28,782
HE WAS ALWAYS TRYING
TO CUDDLE WITH ME AND STUFF.

240
00:14:28,816 --> 00:14:30,849
[GASPS]
COME ON, YOU DID.
DON'T DENY IT.

241
00:14:30,882 --> 00:14:33,949
- WOULD YOU STOP IT?
- HE WANTED TO MARRY ME.

242
00:14:33,982 --> 00:14:36,849
HE EVEN MADE AN ENGAGEMENT RING
FOR ME OUT OF LOTUS FLOWERS.

243
00:14:36,882 --> 00:14:38,816
- GEEZ, CUT IT OUT!
- [LAUGHING]

244
00:14:38,849 --> 00:14:42,882
HE WAS ALL,
"PLEASE, MARRY ME.
PLEASE. <i>PLEASE."</i>

245
00:14:50,982 --> 00:14:53,782
IT'S GOING TO TAKE
A LOT OF WORK,
THAT'S FOR SURE.

246
00:14:53,816 --> 00:14:55,549
BUT IT'S NOT IMPOSSIBLE.

247
00:14:55,582 --> 00:14:58,682
YOU CAN REALLY FIX IT?
MAYBE.

248
00:14:58,716 --> 00:15:00,649
IN ORDER TO FORGE
A JAPANESE SWORD,

249
00:15:00,682 --> 00:15:04,782
YOU NEED IRON SAND
SMELTED IN A FURNACE AT
A SPECIFIC TEMPERATURE.

250
00:15:04,816 --> 00:15:07,649
THE PROCESS IS
A LITTLE DIFFERENT
FOR DEMON SWORDS THOUGH.

251
00:15:07,682 --> 00:15:11,182
YOU HAVE TO INFUSE
THE IRON SAND WITH SPIRITUAL
POWER THROUGH A RITUAL.

252
00:15:11,216 --> 00:15:13,882
BUT HERE'S THE PROBLEM--
I DON'T KNOW ANYONE...

253
00:15:13,916 --> 00:15:16,549
WHO REMEMBERS HOW TO PERFORM
THAT RITUAL ANYMORE.

254
00:15:16,582 --> 00:15:18,649
AND THERE ARE NO RECORDS
OF IT LEFT ANYWHERE?

255
00:15:18,682 --> 00:15:24,149
HMM-MM. IT'S NOT POSSIBLE
TO MAKE A DEMON SWORD
ANY OTHER WAY.

256
00:15:24,182 --> 00:15:27,616
I WISH I KNEW ANOTHER.
[SIGHS]
SO WE CAME HERE FOR NOTHING?

257
00:15:27,649 --> 00:15:32,016
OKAY, WE DON'T KNOW THE RITUAL,
BUT WHAT IF YOU HAD IRON SAND
THAT HAD ALREADY BEEN BLESSED?

258
00:15:32,049 --> 00:15:34,782
I GUESS IF I GOT
MY HANDS ON SOME.

259
00:15:34,816 --> 00:15:36,882
BUT WHERE WOULD WE FIND
SOMETHING LIKE THAT NOW?

260
00:15:36,916 --> 00:15:39,849
DO YOU THINK YOU COULD USE
THOSE TEMPLE NAILS?

261
00:15:39,882 --> 00:15:41,816
[YOSHIKUNI]
WHAT TEMPLE NAILS?

262
00:15:41,849 --> 00:15:44,149
[SUGURO]
THERE USED TO BE A TOWER
AS OLD AS OUR TEMPLE.

263
00:15:44,182 --> 00:15:46,982
WHEN THE BLUE NIGHT HAPPENED,
IT BURNED DOWN.

264
00:15:47,016 --> 00:15:50,816
NOTHING WAS LEFT EXCEPT A BUNCH
OF THICK TEMPLE NAILS.

265
00:15:50,849 --> 00:15:56,782
THEY TURNED OUT TO BE PRETTY
VALUABLE, SO WE DECIDED TO KEEP
THEM AT OUR SISTER TEMPLE.

266
00:15:56,816 --> 00:16:01,616
ANYWAY, LONG STORY SHORT,
THOSE NAILS WERE MADE
BY THE YOSHIKUNIS, RIGHT?

267
00:16:01,649 --> 00:16:05,649
SO THERE'S A CHANCE THEY WERE
MADE WITH THE SAME IRON SAND
USED FOR THE SWORD.

268
00:16:05,682 --> 00:16:09,149
[YOSHIKUNI] WELL, MAYBE
KURIKARA AND THE NAILS WERE
MADE FROM THE SAME STUFF.

269
00:16:09,182 --> 00:16:12,316
[YUKIO]
THEN IF WE CAN GET OUR HANDS
ON THOSE TEMPLE NAILS--

270
00:16:12,349 --> 00:16:15,116
[YOSHIKUNI]
I MIGHT BE ABLE
TO FIX THE SWORD.

271
00:16:17,582 --> 00:16:19,249
[SHIMA]
ANYBODY HOME?

272
00:16:19,282 --> 00:16:21,849
HELLO?

273
00:16:21,882 --> 00:16:24,282
THAT'S WEIRD.
ARE THEY AT LUNCH?

274
00:16:24,316 --> 00:16:26,616
HMM.
OH, WELL.
LET'S HAVE A LOOK AROUND.

275
00:16:26,649 --> 00:16:28,982
I'M GONNA CHECK
THE MAIN HALL.

276
00:16:29,016 --> 00:16:30,482
MIND IF I GO
WITH YOU?

277
00:16:37,549 --> 00:16:39,649
LOOKS LIKE NOBODY'S HOME.

278
00:16:39,682 --> 00:16:41,949
I'M GONNA GO OUT BACK
AND CHECK THE CHARNEL HOUSE.

279
00:16:41,982 --> 00:16:44,449
YOU WAIT HERE FOR ME,
OKAY, TEACH?

280
00:16:44,482 --> 00:16:45,949
[CICADAS BUZZING]

281
00:16:45,982 --> 00:16:48,382
[SHIMA]
HELLO?
IS ANYONE AROUND?

282
00:16:48,416 --> 00:16:50,649
HEY, ANYONE?
HELLO?
[GASPS]

283
00:16:50,682 --> 00:16:52,249
[SHIEMI]
OVER THERE!

284
00:16:55,116 --> 00:16:57,216
OH, PLEASE TELL ME
THAT GUY ISN'T DEAD.

285
00:16:57,249 --> 00:16:59,816
HE'S OKAY.
HE'S JUST UNCONSCIOUS, IS ALL.

286
00:16:59,849 --> 00:17:02,249
[GASPS]
LOOK! SO ARE THEY.

287
00:17:07,616 --> 00:17:09,549
[MALE VOICE]
WHAT'S WRONG?

288
00:17:09,582 --> 00:17:13,316
YOU WANT TO KILL SATAN,
DON'T YOU?

289
00:17:13,349 --> 00:17:14,549
[GASPS]

290
00:17:14,582 --> 00:17:16,682
[FEMALE VOICE]
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

291
00:17:16,716 --> 00:17:20,182
WHY ARE YOU TRYING SO HARD
TO SAVE A DEMON?

292
00:17:20,216 --> 00:17:23,482
DON'T LIE.
I KNOW WHAT YOU'RE FEELING.

293
00:17:23,516 --> 00:17:25,182
YOU KNOW NOTHING.

294
00:17:25,216 --> 00:17:27,016
BE HONEST WITH YOURSELF.

295
00:17:27,049 --> 00:17:29,949
HE IS THE SON OF SATAN
AFTER ALL.

296
00:17:29,982 --> 00:17:32,882
THE WORLD WOULD BE
BETTER OFF WITHOUT HIM.

297
00:17:32,916 --> 00:17:34,982
ISN'T THAT HOW YOU FEEL?

298
00:17:35,016 --> 00:17:39,216
ARE YOU SURE YOU WANT TO SAVE
THE SON OF SATAN?

299
00:17:39,249 --> 00:17:43,282
WHY? BECAUSE YOU HAPPEN
TO BE RELATED BY BLOOD?

300
00:17:43,316 --> 00:17:44,749
ARE YOU A DEMON?

301
00:17:44,782 --> 00:17:48,216
YOU KNOW I AM NOT THE ONE
YOU HAVE TO DEFEAT.

302
00:17:48,249 --> 00:17:54,416
DEEP IN YOUR HEART,
YOU KNOW WHO YOU FEAR THE MOST--
YOUR BROTHER.

303
00:17:54,449 --> 00:17:59,449
AS LONG AS HE LIVES,
YOU WILL ALWAYS LIVE
IN FEAR OF HIS POWER.

304
00:17:59,482 --> 00:18:02,449
OF HIM.
I ASK AGAIN--

305
00:18:02,482 --> 00:18:04,816
WHY ARE YOU TRYING TO SAVE HIM?

306
00:18:04,849 --> 00:18:09,216
WHAT REASON IS THERE
FOR SAVING THE SON OF SATAN?

307
00:18:09,249 --> 00:18:11,016
REASON.

308
00:18:11,049 --> 00:18:15,549
DO YOU REMEMBER WHAT HAPPENED
TO YOUR TEMPLE BECAUSE OF SATAN?

309
00:18:15,582 --> 00:18:18,549
WHY THEN SHOULD YOU SAVE
HIS SON?

310
00:18:18,582 --> 00:18:20,416
[EXHALES]

311
00:18:20,449 --> 00:18:22,349
[GASPS]

312
00:18:22,382 --> 00:18:24,682
WHY MAKE YOUR LIFE HARDER?

313
00:18:24,716 --> 00:18:27,516
ALL YOU NEED DO
IS TURN YOUR BACK.

314
00:18:27,549 --> 00:18:29,182
LET THE ORDER
GET RID OF YOUR BROTHER,

315
00:18:29,216 --> 00:18:33,116
AND THEN YOU CAN LIVE
THE REST OF YOUR LIFE
WITHOUT FEAR.

316
00:18:35,982 --> 00:18:38,716
- HEY, TEACH!
- SHIMA.

317
00:18:42,082 --> 00:18:43,282
[GASPS]

318
00:18:43,316 --> 00:18:45,582
[GRUNTS]

319
00:18:45,616 --> 00:18:47,649
- [GUN COCKS]
- YOU'RE WRONG.

320
00:18:47,682 --> 00:18:50,116
MY BROTHER ISN'T THE ONE
I'M AFRAID OF.

321
00:18:50,149 --> 00:18:54,082
I'M SCARED
I WON'T BE STRONG ENOUGH
TO PROTECT HIM WHEN HE NEEDS ME.

322
00:18:54,116 --> 00:18:57,816
I SWORE I'D BECOME
A STRONGER PERSON JUST SO
I COULD PROTECT MY BROTHER.

323
00:18:57,849 --> 00:19:00,082
I SWORE I'D PROTECT HIM.

324
00:19:05,516 --> 00:19:08,082
[SIGHS, PANTS]

325
00:19:12,149 --> 00:19:14,082
BEGONE, DEMON!

326
00:19:15,649 --> 00:19:17,049
SUGURO!

327
00:19:17,082 --> 00:19:18,149
[GASPS]

328
00:19:18,182 --> 00:19:19,816
[GROWLS]

329
00:19:19,849 --> 00:19:23,182
YOU WANT A REASON?
I GOT ONE FOR YA.

330
00:19:23,216 --> 00:19:26,216
IN THE MIDDLE OF CLASS,
HE TELLS ME HE WANTS TO BE
AN EXORCIST...

331
00:19:26,249 --> 00:19:29,682
SO HE CAN KICK SATAN'S ASS,
AND HE'S THE FRIGGIN' SON
OF SATAN.

332
00:19:29,716 --> 00:19:32,982
I NEVER HEARD ANYTHING
SO TWISTED IN MY LIFE.

333
00:19:33,016 --> 00:19:35,416
SO IF HE DIES
BEFORE I CAN ASK HIM
WHAT HE MEANT,

334
00:19:35,449 --> 00:19:37,549
I'LL BE PISSED!

335
00:19:37,582 --> 00:19:39,949
[CHANTING IN FOREIGN LANGUAGE]

336
00:19:44,482 --> 00:19:46,849
[SIGHS, PANTS]

337
00:19:53,182 --> 00:19:55,249
[SUGURO]
THE HEAD PRIEST IS SAFE.

338
00:19:55,282 --> 00:19:57,249
GOOD. I'M GLAD.

339
00:19:57,282 --> 00:19:59,882
THE DEMON WE CONFRONTED,
IT WAS MARA, WASN'T IT?

340
00:19:59,916 --> 00:20:03,349
YES. MARA TRIED
TO DISTRACT SIDDHARTHA...

341
00:20:03,382 --> 00:20:06,049
WHILE HE WAS MEDITATING
TO REACH ENLIGHTENMENT.

342
00:20:06,082 --> 00:20:09,649
PREYING ON A PERSON'S DOUBTS
AND WEAKNESSES, HUH? TYPICAL.

343
00:20:09,682 --> 00:20:12,416
I REMEMBER HEARING
ABOUT DEMONS LIKE MARA...

344
00:20:12,449 --> 00:20:15,982
AND HOW THEY POSSESS
THE BUDDHIST STATUES
IN OLD TEMPLES.

345
00:20:16,016 --> 00:20:18,682
I BROUGHT THE TEMPLE NAILS
YOU ASKED FOR.

346
00:20:18,716 --> 00:20:20,782
GREAT. THANK YOU.

347
00:20:29,116 --> 00:20:31,916
HE PLANNED TO BETRAY THE ORDER
AND DESTROY IT FROM WITHIN.

348
00:20:31,949 --> 00:20:34,049
THERE CAN BE NO DOUBT
ABOUT MEPHISTO'S TREACHERY.

349
00:20:34,082 --> 00:20:39,882
BUT EVEN SO, THE ORDER HAS NEVER
HAD A WEAPON POWERFUL ENOUGH
TO DEFEAT SATAN AND HIS ARMIES.

350
00:20:39,916 --> 00:20:42,982
THE MAGNITUDE OF THIS ISSUE
IS UNPRECEDENTED.

351
00:20:43,016 --> 00:20:46,149
AN ERROR IN JUDGMENT
COULD SPELL THE END
OF THE ORDER.

352
00:20:46,182 --> 00:20:49,249
[THINKING]
DAMN, HOW LONG
ARE THEY GONNA KEEP YAPPING?

353
00:20:49,282 --> 00:20:52,316
- [RUMBLING]
- [SHURA]
WHAT IS HAPPENING?

354
00:20:52,349 --> 00:20:54,816
[CHUCKLES]
DAMN HIM.

355
00:20:54,849 --> 00:20:58,416
[AMAIMON]
WHERE IS HE?
TELL ME WHERE HE IS.

356
00:20:58,449 --> 00:21:01,049
I HAVEN'T LOST THE BATTLE YET.

357
00:21:09,116 --> 00:21:10,682
[FEMALE GRIGORI]
AMAIMON?

358
00:21:10,716 --> 00:21:13,749
HOW DID HE GET IN HERE?

359
00:21:13,782 --> 00:21:16,516
- [MAN]
ANGEL!
- YES, SIR.

360
00:21:16,549 --> 00:21:19,482
SIR PHELES,
ARE YOU BEHIND THIS?

361
00:21:19,516 --> 00:21:21,416
YOU JEST, MILORD.

362
00:21:21,449 --> 00:21:25,416
WHAT ON EARTH WOULD I HAVE
TO GAIN BY CAUSING SUCH MISCHIEF
AT MY OWN HEARING?

363
00:21:25,449 --> 00:21:30,749
THAT BEING SAID, MIGHT I SUGGEST
WE TAKE ADVANTAGE
OF THIS GOLDEN OPPORTUNITY.

364
00:21:30,782 --> 00:21:33,116
INSTEAD OF TALKING
ABOUT HIS POTENTIAL,

365
00:21:33,149 --> 00:21:36,316
SEE FOR YOURSELVES
JUST HOW POWERFUL
THE SPAWN OF SATAN IS.

366
00:21:36,349 --> 00:21:39,482
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?
[MEPHISTO]
WE ARE UNDER SIEGE, MILADY.

367
00:21:39,516 --> 00:21:44,449
AND CURRENTLY THE BOY
IS THE ONLY WEAPON
POWERFUL ENOUGH TO PROTECT US.

368
00:21:44,482 --> 00:21:49,949
WHO WOULD LIKE TO BET
ON WHETHER RIN OKUMURA BECOMES
THE SAVIOR OF ASSIAH...

369
00:21:49,982 --> 00:21:53,082
OR HE BECOMES THE DEMON KING
OF GEHENNA?

370
00:21:53,116 --> 00:21:56,816
WOULDN'T YOU LIKE TO SEE
THE OUTCOME
WITH YOUR VERY OWN EYES?

371
00:22:06,816 --> 00:22:09,716
♪ [WOMAN SINGING
IN JAPANESE]

372
00:23:35,016 --> 00:23:36,516
MM-HMM.

373
00:23:36,549 --> 00:23:38,382
RIGHT.
THIS IS GOING TO WORK.

374
00:23:38,416 --> 00:23:40,716
- [GASPING]
- YEAH!

375
00:23:54,149 --> 00:23:55,849
[RUMBLING]

376
00:24:03,082 --> 00:24:05,549
[MEPHISTO]
NO PRESSURE, BUT THE POLLS
WILL BE CLOSING SOON.

377
00:24:05,582 --> 00:24:08,716
TIME TO CAST YOUR VOTES--
YEA OR NAY.

378
00:24:08,749 --> 00:24:13,349
- [YUKIO] YOU FIEND!
- [AMAIMON] I'VE COME TO
SETTLE THINGS, RIN OKUMURA.

379
00:24:13,382 --> 00:24:15,316
[YUKIO]
WAKE UP!

